OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOrkney will be cloudy with rain
OL,6,Fat times, although turning drier
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon. Dry across
OL,8,FShetland this morning before
OL,9,Foccasional rain spreads north this
OL,10,Fafternoon. Fresh to strong
OL,11,Fsoutheasterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night to
OL,14,Fcome with spells of rain and drizzle.
OL,15,FSome misty low cloud developing. Fresh
OL,16,Fto strong southeasterly winds easing
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
