OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy with some showery
OL,6,Frain at times, but some drier
OL,7,Finterludes too. Chance of haar across
OL,8,FShetland.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FMainly dry on Thursday, a few light
OL,12,Fafternoon showers spreading north.
OL,13,FRain at times on Friday, drier later.
OL,14,FDry on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
